      "writtenOn": "2017-09-21T19:21:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is this really sufficient? With stuff like swarming_tag one would need a yet another parser to yet another separate type to hold swarming_tag data. I don\u0027t know if swarming_tag is going to even stay, but if it is it might be worth making this map[string]map[string]string, or turning it into a tree.",
