      "message": "hierarchical tags are more of an exception than a rule, so I am not sure I want to complicate this API for this rare case. \n\nHaving said that, I think it is sufficientish:\n\n  swarming_tags \u003d ParseTags(ParseTags(rawtags)[\"swarming_tag\"])\n\nWDYT?",
